{"title":"Our pledge for the HDR UK Black Internship programme","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Our pledge for the HDR UK Black Internship programme","description":"Cohort and medical record data will allow us to look in depth at who with severe or complex mental illness attends key physical health screening programmes","image":"laptop.jpg","categories":["Collaborations"],"author":"Naomi Launders","date":"10/09/2025","toc":false},"headingText":"Our pledge for the HDR UK Black Internship programme","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n\nThis week we submitted our pledge for the [HDR UK Black Internship programme](https://www.hdruk.ac.uk/study-and-train/train/health-data-science-black-internship-programme/). This programme offers a paid 8-week internship in data science, alongside training, networking and collaborative opportunities.\n\nI don't yet know what our project will be - something around the intersection of physical and mental health. We'll be hosting the successful applicant in the Division of Psychiatry and in the Advanced Research Computing department - both at UCL. I think being based across these two departments should lead to a really broad and interesting experience.\n\nWatch this space for more information!\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n## Our pledge for the HDR UK Black Internship programme\n\nThis week we submitted our pledge for the [HDR UK Black Internship programme](https://www.hdruk.ac.uk/study-and-train/train/health-data-science-black-internship-programme/). This programme offers a paid 8-week internship in data science, alongside training, networking and collaborative opportunities.\n\nI don't yet know what our project will be - something around the intersection of physical and mental health. We'll be hosting the successful applicant in the Division of Psychiatry and in the Advanced Research Computing department - both at UCL. I think being based across these two departments should lead to a really broad and interesting experience.\n\nWatch this space for more information!\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","css":["../../styles.css"],"toc":false,"output-file":"index.html"},"language":{"toc-title-document":"Table of contents","toc-title-website":"On this page","related-formats-title":"Other Formats","related-notebooks-title":"Notebooks","source-notebooks-prefix":"Source","other-links-title":"Other Links","code-links-title":"Code Links","launch-dev-container-title":"Launch Dev Container","launch-binder-title":"Launch Binder","article-notebook-label":"Article Notebook","notebook-preview-download":"Download Notebook","notebook-preview-download-src":"Download Source","notebook-preview-back":"Back to Article","man